These hip adduction & abduction machines I definitely kind of neglect but not anymore…adduction is when your limbs are moving towards your center line and abduction is when they’re moving away from your centerline (as shown here). Abduction generally strengthens the gluteal muscles and this can alleviate back pain. Hip abductors are important for physical movement.

Warrior Family ! Quick message I think a lot of you may need to hear. This is personally something I used to struggle with myself. Listen up 👂 everyday you will not be able to do the same weight or amount of reps on exercises etc. There is a lot of factors that goes into that, such as amount of sleep, meals you ate or didn’t eat before the gym, water intake etc. Your energy levels and muscles are different.  The most important thing is you show up relentlessly and give everything you have and go as hard as you possibly can. That’s all we can do. #WarriorMindset 💪⚔️🧠♾️🧬📈
